  "detailed_description": "Kodon is a VR/Desktop sculpting software <strong>under development</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/fb7c0c0e9b9c52c3e84edd4116393ed0.poster.avif?t=1704150000\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/fb7c0c0e9b9c52c3e84edd4116393ed0.webm?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/fb7c0c0e9b9c52c3e84edd4116393ed0.mp4?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>We use the word <strong>feel</strong> to describe the effect we are striving towards with Kodon. This word describes speed, intuitivity, inspiration and enjoyment.  We support all Meta/Oculus headsets, the mainstream SteamVR based (Vive, Index), and WMR sets (HP Reverb, WMR). We also try to get more rare headsets working. Contact us on Discord and help us make your headset work!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f44baf556c6ef426fee46362fce5d8c1.poster.avif?t=1704150000\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f44baf556c6ef426fee46362fce5d8c1.webm?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f44baf556c6ef426fee46362fce5d8c1.mp4?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Kodon innovated the \"hybrid workflow\". By adding desktop workflow, we allow you to switch effortlessly between immersion and overview, and between free-drawing and flat (\"planar\") approaches to your work. We want to be fully competitive with the existing desktop alternatives for asset creation,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f1e8651342c06df4fb4d4b86571d6d3f.poster.avif?t=1704150000\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f1e8651342c06df4fb4d4b86571d6d3f.webm?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f1e8651342c06df4fb4d4b86571d6d3f.mp4?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Visit our Discord chat and tell us what works, what doesn't, and what you want to see in the future for Kodon.",
  "about_the_game": "Kodon is a VR/Desktop sculpting software <strong>under development</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/fb7c0c0e9b9c52c3e84edd4116393ed0.poster.avif?t=1704150000\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/fb7c0c0e9b9c52c3e84edd4116393ed0.webm?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/fb7c0c0e9b9c52c3e84edd4116393ed0.mp4?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>We use the word <strong>feel</strong> to describe the effect we are striving towards with Kodon. This word describes speed, intuitivity, inspiration and enjoyment.  We support all Meta/Oculus headsets, the mainstream SteamVR based (Vive, Index), and WMR sets (HP Reverb, WMR). We also try to get more rare headsets working. Contact us on Discord and help us make your headset work!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f44baf556c6ef426fee46362fce5d8c1.poster.avif?t=1704150000\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f44baf556c6ef426fee46362fce5d8c1.webm?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f44baf556c6ef426fee46362fce5d8c1.mp4?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Kodon innovated the \"hybrid workflow\". By adding desktop workflow, we allow you to switch effortlessly between immersion and overview, and between free-drawing and flat (\"planar\") approaches to your work. We want to be fully competitive with the existing desktop alternatives for asset creation,<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f1e8651342c06df4fb4d4b86571d6d3f.poster.avif?t=1704150000\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f1e8651342c06df4fb4d4b86571d6d3f.webm?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/479010/extras/f1e8651342c06df4fb4d4b86571d6d3f.mp4?t=1704150000\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Visit our Discord chat and tell us what works, what doesn't, and what you want to see in the future for Kodon.",
